Package: tiler
Type: Package
Version: 0.0.0.2
Title: Tiles for visualizing large spatial data
Description: Create tiles for visualizing large spatial data sets in leaflet
    or shiny applications. Note that this package requires python (version 2.7)
    and the gdal python package to be installed.
